* :-hcP2Py: such as stating, questioning, commanding, promising, etc.  Not all illocutionary acts have propositional content (e.g. ``hurrah!'').  Note that illocutionary negation is distinct from propositional negation (for example: ``I do not promise to come'' versus ``I promise not to come'').
